:::Scourge/Hun-Grr/Ramjet:::

Scourge: Hey, hey, take it easy. I was just asking your name. My names 
Scourge, whats yours?
~~~~~
::Hun-Grr is tired of trying to keep his team from fighting, so he just sits 
down and watches Rippersnapper and Sinnertwin::
~~~~~
::Ramjet nods::
Ramjet: Allow me to introduce my team:  These are my gestalt partners, Dirge 
and Skywarp, the two jets are Falcon and Snare, the strange looking one is 
Like-Like, my right hand man and tactical advisor is Cygnar, and the last one 
is Neody.  I think Cygnar and i should discuss with you.  May we start now?

--part1_c9.e4ebcd3.27ee19cc_boundary
